::Incarcinator::

Incarcinator smiles, firing three shells at Beastbox. One of them
missed and hit the ground along with the earlier three, making a large
explosion to greet Beasbox.

> Beastbox grunted at the fact that Incinerator was flying upwards. He

maneuvered

beside
> him. He then began his decent towards the hard, coming up fast
ground.
